Algorithmic basis
-----------------
The pegRNA design procedure implements the approach described in:

  Lin, Q., Jin, S., Zong, Y. et al. High-efficiency prime editing with optimized
  extended pegRNAs in rice and wheat. Nature Biotechnology 39, 923-927 (2021).
  https://doi.org/10.1038/s41587-021-00868-w


