----------------------
Bundled or integrated third-party software retains its own original license:

  - pegLIT — BSD 3-Clause (Broad Institute & Harvard, 2023)
    See: ext_tools/peglit/LICENSE
    Nelson, J.W. et al. Nature Biotechnology 40, 402-410 (2022).

  - PRIDICT2.0 — MIT (Krauthammer Lab & Schwank Lab)
    See: ext_tools/PRIDICT2/LICENSE
    Mathis, N. et al. Nature Biotechnology (2024).

  - pegFinder — MIT (Copyright (c) 2020 rdchow)
    The PE3/PE3b nicking-sgRNA logic in peg_core.py is a port of pegFinder; the
    upstream MIT copyright and permission notice is retained inline in that file.
    Chow, R.D. et al. Nature Biomedical Engineering 5, 190-194 (2021).
